    "description": "如果您想在敌人中斩杀和冲刺，与难缠的老板战斗并收集独特的物品，那么这款 2D roguelike 动作游戏适合您。 这是你要做的......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/8570331ffb123e0e831f74080fe77e3e.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>[h2使用不同的战斗技能来帮助你生存[/h2]</u></strong><br>使用不同的战斗技能进行砍杀、砍杀、射击、躲避、冲刺和格挡，以击败敌人和老板。但这并不全是无意识的战斗。 <br>如果你想生存，就必须注意不同的敌人，学习他们的模式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/5994bfb6f025e7c7695b1ee88b6756bf.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在每次奔跑中收集不同的能力</strong></h2></u><br>每一次奔跑都是不同的，因为你永远不知道自己会在旅途中获得什么独特的能力。 你可以收集760种独特的能力，帮助你在奔跑中生存下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/81a66de4f910986dc0bb403292e2904f.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择一个与您的游戏风格相得益彰的伴侣</h2></u></strong><br>为了帮助你在王国中奋力拼搏，有26个独特的同伴可供你选择。 而且因为每个同伴都是独一无二的，你可以选择一个符合你的游戏风格。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/83142d705c755e6fca62288823aa6ece.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/83142d705c755e6fca62288823aa6ece.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/83142d705c755e6fca62288823aa6ece.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >12个不同的级别</h2></u></strong><br>关卡排列在战区。在每个战区中，你都可以与一群粘人战斗。 一旦你清除了粘液，你就会与一个老板战斗。 <br>你的奖励？你会遇到一个商人，在那里你可以购买战利品来帮助你 下一个战区。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/317d9866aed2ce2132a9400e001e73e2.webp?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=47 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/91da886886995f952a5a0fe65bb79801.poster.avif?t=1746818790\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/91da886886995f952a5a0fe65bb79801.webm?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276960/extras/91da886886995f952a5a0fe65bb79801.mp4?t=1746818790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >12 场独特而困难的 Boss 战</h2></u></strong><br>你面对的每个老板都有自己独特的模式，你需要掌握这些模式。不同的老板需要不同的战术。 因此，您旅程的一部分是学习这些老板并根据每个老板调整您的技能。<br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢您查看我的游戏！</h2></u></strong><br>嘿，我叫Velemir，在瑞士。 我是一名个人游戏开发者，将 A Land Goo's Crazy 作为一个充满激情的项目。 <br>我在 Pixel Game Maker MV 中编写了游戏代码。我自己做了艺术。 我的兄弟帮助制作了令人惊叹的音乐和配乐。 <br>无论如何，非常感谢您查看我的游戏！ 我希望你在玩游戏时玩得开心，并试图弄清楚游戏背后的黑暗传说和奥秘。<br><br>- 韦勒米尔",
